Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.32,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}BON-BON Cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:51.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:03.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:10.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:22.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:02.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:03.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:33.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw a shooting star the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:38.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Kagami said something about the\Nwishing three times thing being unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:40.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to see the stars from our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:46.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:48.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since your house is in the city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I would probably be too amazed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to have time to make a wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:55.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of a dazzling, shining star...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:58.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...would fill you with feelings of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:01.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That could explain the myth that shooting stars grant wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:06.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your honesty is what dazzles me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost winter break.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have finals first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:16.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any plans for winter break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:18.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:18.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't taken a vacation in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Asakusa the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:25.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you get sleepy on the train during winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:30.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She missed her stop?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:31.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that the opposite direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:36.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The train reached the end of the line and turned around...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then I missed my stop again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:40.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time I came to, we were in Asakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:41.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:44.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only miss your stop so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't entirely a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.92,0:02:51.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I hadn't visited Asakusa in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:54.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't be doing that right before finals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:03:00.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I had a feeling I saw a girl in a\Nsailor uniform with a machine gun walk by...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me someone was making a hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping more helps you grow more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:09.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're growing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.99,0:03:11.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an even better one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad pulled an all-nighter and then went to turn in a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He got on an early-morning train but missed his stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...then it reached the end and made a U-turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and when he woke up, he'd already missed his stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this happened a few more times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:27.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He started to wake up when he got close to his station...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:29.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but he still ended up missing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.29,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Patrasche...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:29.77,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I'm so tired...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:34.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He was tired and wanted to get\Nhome and sleep, but he couldn't get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:37.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he no longer knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:42.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which direction he was going whenever he woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:48.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I still wake up before my stop when I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she has an internal alarm clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:55.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it doesn't work all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's always snacking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But train seats are really warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:04.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you get really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all warm and fuzzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:10.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...like you're sitting next to the window in the classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:11.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...on a sunny winter afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:12.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Covering for each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I tried to wake you up on the ride home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:21.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just five more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:25.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She yelled out half-asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around us was laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:33.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One of my friends did that in class once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are so similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:37.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're grouping us together?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you went to wake someone up\Nand they were like, give me another hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't you be pissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:50.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but five minutes comes up in a lot of other situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:52.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, just wait five minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:56.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe 'cause it isn't too long or too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though the five-minute wait for a train feels really long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:00.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:04.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People who say to wait five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...tend to make you wait a lot longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:13.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how people say to not use\Nyour cell or put on makeup on the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:18.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a lot worse when the person next to you leans on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you end up wanting to stand after managing to get a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:28.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you're stuck with the sticky head of an old person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:31.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I try to shove them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:36.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they somehow manage to\Nkeep returning to the same position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:37.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I fall asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:44.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and there's a man on one side and an empty seat on the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I try to lean myself towards the empty seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:50.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but for some reason, I always end up leaning the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:54.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess your body feels more comfortable leaning a certain way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see someone leaning over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I shrink up like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:02.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...then their elbow hits my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean they're actually awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:06.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:07.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...some people at our school take the inbound train home...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and some people take the outbound train home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:22.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the ones who take the\Ninbound train look more refined somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Yuki-chan's an inbounder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:25.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:29.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to the farm, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:52.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the stop before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:05.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get any studying done yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:09.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually put in a lot of effort this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:10.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:13.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How much studying did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Only four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}A whole four hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:21.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at everything, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:24.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do a lot of studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely really competitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:30.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's my pride as the older sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:36.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I have to be ahead of Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I usually say neither of us is really older or younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be pretty worried about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:45.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But Tsukasa probably wasn't much competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's just like Kona-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:54.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what my present will be this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:56.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still get presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long did you believe in Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Claus isn't real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:05.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:09.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa never came to Konata's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:12.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so her dad gave her presents in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:15.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she thought he might be out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:18.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He really wants to look good in front of his daughter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:23.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the handout from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:24.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, Hiiragi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:28.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your pencil.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:33.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:34.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the handout from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:37.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sebastian, like, stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:41.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped your handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:43.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:47.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I go to Tsukasa's class a little too much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:51.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My cavity started hurting recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My, how dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't stand dentists.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to see the dentist for your cavity the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:04.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentists take a long time on each tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they have to repeat the procedure for every tooth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:09.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so it takes a long time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:12.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I ended up escaping...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...after making a number of excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though she sounded all cute...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:18.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that's actually pretty crazy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:23.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go wild with everyone on Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:25.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have plans for Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:29.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going somewhere with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:33.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Dad that I'd be home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:37.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:39.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really going on a date with your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.56,0:09:42.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm just working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:48.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost all the customers are male, so I wasn't lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought you'd managed to get ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a special event on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:57.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We dress like Santa CIaus for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:59.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love that kind of stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:01.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:05.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys also cosplay as shrine maidens for New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At your temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:07.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call it cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:10.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that Santa Claus gives everyone presents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:17.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but ever since I was little, I was like, he's totally trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't look down on something based on a holy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiteful brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:22.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:28.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa is supposed to give children dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:32.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so what's with the men who turn\Nto this little kid with their dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You just casually insulted a lot of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:39.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And is it okay for you guys to celebrate Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:39.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We usually got Christmas presents, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We worship every god there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We regularly visit temples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:51.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we sang in a church choir once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:54.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:55.49,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:11:00.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A shrine maiden said she wanted\Nto get married in a wedding dress...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't that be a little complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.51,0:11:09.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting chilly these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:13.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:14.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:16.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Any good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:18.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That man's the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something odd about this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing odd at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:31.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:35.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why cops are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aren't you a cop yourself...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd someone have to call now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're about to reveal the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:46.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the killer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No use in hiding it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:54.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why these two-hour\Nshows always end on the edge of a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:59.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe cause people aren't willing to\Nact until their back's against the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui, evenin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha watchin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A movie for a popular detective show.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimes don't happen in conference rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They happen at the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody ever gets that passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're going to deny this too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:24.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the receipts were stolen at the behest of the chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:26.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why he fails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:29.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They eat pork bowls a lot in police shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but apparently, that isn't actually allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:34.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so a lot of it's probably made-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:40.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So police commissioners' granddaughters aren't really like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Police commissioners' granddaughters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've never met one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd at least want Mai-chan to exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To give me hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:49.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Empty dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of cases with adults going after children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:59.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you taught kids martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:02.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't there be a decrease in that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:04.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After intensive training...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:08.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Master Oyama was able to beat a\Ncow with his bare hands, with one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And bears toppled like trees after a couple of hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:16.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But won't that come back to haunt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When those kids grow up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the adults will be strong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:21.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People say training in the martial arts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...helps you mature as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:34.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who does martial\Narts and hasn't matured right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:36.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:41.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this cousin, Cousin Yui's little\N sister, who's entering high school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:43.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's physically weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:46.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she's sweet and pure and really adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.62,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Cousin Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:53.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I start thinking about how a\Nhealthy spirit leads to a healthy body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:58.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,....I start feeling like something dark\Nis lurking behind those shining eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt aphorisms are universal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:02.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:04.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The year's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:07.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's December, you always feel like the year flew by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:12.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to help out at your\Ntemple as shrine maidens again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come draw your fortune again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With fortunes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:20.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get really bad luck, it's an unpleasant feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:21.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you get really good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it feels like you already wasted\Nyour luck for the year, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:27.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's why people say average luck is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:31.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then here's an early present from your teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:32.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are your report cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.60,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Here! Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this present!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We give presents based on effort in my school of Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:44.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Think on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bonus to your winter homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:51.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of Christmas cakes will be good this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to a bakery...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are so many cute cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you can have fun just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:15:00.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to the cakes that aren't sold before Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:04.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps the employees take them home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:08.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if nobody takes them, they might throw them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They often compare marriage to Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how twenty-five is the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:18.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're past twenty-five,\Na Christmas cake is just another cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After one night, it's just another decorated cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:22.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...that suddenly looks stale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you lose your appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking about Santa Claus with Kona-chan the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long did you believe in Santa, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:34.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like you would have been a true believer like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:37.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also believed in Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:41.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I tried to send a\Nletter of gratitude to Santa Claus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and did some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:47.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't learn much after asking my parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I did some thorough investigating...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:51.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and learned of the people Santa Claus was based on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.51,0:15:54.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and once I saw the phrase "origin of Santa Claus" pop up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...my dreams were quickly shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you do, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.39,0:16:04.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you would expect from Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a little pissed about losing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:12.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan's at the top of our class, so it's hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We could never beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:15.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about grades...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:17.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but stuff like bust size...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm hungry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have a cup of ramen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not done yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:28.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These three minutes of waiting feel really long.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use this to kill time today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:35.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then your noodles end up soggy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:35.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The extra broth for my cup fried soba dried up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You people...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:45.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She told me she would be late...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:46.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is too late!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:48.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't let her make a habit of this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:50.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Need to give her a stern dressing down every now and then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As the man of the house.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:53.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:56.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What time do you think it i—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Christmas present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been cold outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some hot tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:05.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:06.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I do! I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,G'day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:15.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui's here to save the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You stink of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:17.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to DUI!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I parked the car somewhere and had a drink nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas Eve yet my husband's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our plans tonight are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:27.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:30.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you go to your parents'\Nplace instead every once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:33.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:33.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to sneak in and surprise you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it was locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you at your parents' place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:40.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Running every light on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:47.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you shouldn't be breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll log in for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:53.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not a leftover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't count as a leftover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'Cause I bought one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was here last Sunday to buy manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get why you pay the fare to come here so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's for the points...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is pretty excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:31.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really love this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:35.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, do you even use the prizes they give?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:41.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of stuff is hard to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:42.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,lt'd be a waste to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Their value would go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:49.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, so that's how it is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:49.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:54.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:55.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.81,0:18:58.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you get shocked by static electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:18:59.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:03.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata's always sitting in front of the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so her body's already full of weird waves?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I really can't stand winter for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:11.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I heard you can get shocked just by touching someone's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:12.69,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,616.5)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:13.49,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,616.5)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:14.15,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,616.5)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.03,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,616.5)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this means you two don't really get along with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:15.91,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(868,631.5)}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanted to try it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:27.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:34.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:40.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on the eleventh episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:42.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And on this eleventh episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:47.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have some wonderful news you've all been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's sent in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.54,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really in it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...lots of passionate letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:57.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...asking for Akira to show up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:57.88,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:59.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode, I, Akira Kogami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.47,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the assistant Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:03.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...will be showing up in the actual show!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.10,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,But I need to introduce myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you to Konata Izumi from\NSaitama along with everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...who sent postcards to Newtype!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Akira-sama's also making an appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:15.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Like, you're finally showing up in the twelfth episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in it for, like, forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:21.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho. Ho. Ho."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...attitude you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:27.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an honor to appear with Akira-sama in the actual show as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All you did this week was pick up a handkerchief, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:37.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be thinking you've got\Nwhat it takes to make it in this business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that you can just disappear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After that announcement...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can't wait for the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:48.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You want it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:49.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is probably trembling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, shaking naked in their boots in anticipation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:52.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We should treat our fans with care...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:57.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and air it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can grab a thirty minute slot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:58.65,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.82,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be pushing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.61,0:21:01.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:03.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So send any messages you have to the radio show or the home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:09.45,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be bad if I overshadowed the main characters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It would indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a tendency for the\Nmain character's friends and rivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:21.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to end up more popular than the actual main characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:23.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:24.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:26.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:26.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:27.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...talking about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:31.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so full of yourself 'cause you're popular lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:33.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect this to last!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:32.21,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No, absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.08,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:36.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be placing first in the poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.24,0:21:36.92,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:38.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.23,0:21:38.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:38.84,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to m—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:50.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we have a duet from Tsukasa and Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:50.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go up front to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:57.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose a song for them to sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all kinds of songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:05.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still an anime song, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.18,0:22:08.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anime songs actually come in handy in these situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:43.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:13.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:15.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:15.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:19.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really hungry one night...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:21.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it was really late...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:24.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I was wondering if I should eat something...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:27.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally decided a little bite would be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:29.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I went to the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.64,0:23:31.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I remembered I had some snacks left over...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:33.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I opened up the freezer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.56,0:23:34.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already out of time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:35.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:37.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Go to the Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.14,0:23:38.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:09.23,ls_episode_title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs60\pos(800,185)}The Many\NWays\Nto Spend\NChristmas\NEve
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.52,ls_single,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1000,34)\blur1\fad(300,0)}Nanako Kuroi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.52,ls_single,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1000,117)\blur1\fad(300,0)}27 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.52,ls_single,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\frz90\pos(16,255)\fad(400,0)}Single
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:18.34,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.34,0:22:20.34,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Really would be so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:22.30,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,This dream! That dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.30,0:22:26.30,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I have so many dreams!
